page.title: 16Wickwar shops
page.content:
THERE ARE STILL SHOPS IN WICKWAR,SPAR,HAIRDRESSERS,THERE IS ONE GARAGE IN WICKWAR. IN WICKWAR THERE IS A VERY INFREEQUENT BUS SERVICE.THERE IS A RAILWAY THAT RUNS THROUGH WICKWAR AND THERE USED TO BE A STATION BUT IT GOT IT WAS KNOCKED DOWN SOMETIME AGO.

JUST ALONG THE ROAD USED TO BE A HOTEL CALLED THE RAILWAY INN,BUT IT WAS CLOSED DOWN AND MADE INTO A PRIVATE HOUSE. JUST OUTSIDE WICKWAR THERE IS A POPULAR NURSERY OR "GARDEN CENTRE"
